Package: xdrxlsx
Type: Package
Title: Minimal DrawingML Graphics Device for openxlsx2
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A base-R graphics device that writes R plots directly as
    OOXML DrawingML shapes, for use with openxlsx2::wb_add_drawing().
    No dependency on Cairo, FreeType, fontconfig, or xml2.
